<br>
I usually just run right off the cliff and if Drakes aggro I follow the beach in as straight a line as I can, eventually the Drakes will go back to their spawn. No problem.<br>
<br>
Just don't stand around long enough to get hit by 2 AEs or you're dead.<br>
<br>
I've found that CT, SF and WL port-in spots are a lot more difficult and risky than CS.<br>
